Package company.taskMan.resource

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvailabilityPeriod
    The AvailabilityPeriod of a resource indicates when that resource is available during the day.
    ConcreteResource
    This class represents "concrete" resources.
    PrototypeManager  
    Reservation
    A reservation will link a resource (a concrete resource or a user) with a task (reserving the resource).
    Resource
    This abstract class defines resources.
    ResourceManager
    The resource manager is the part in the system that will keep the data about resources, users and reservations.
    ResourcePool
    A resource pool is a collection of concrete resources based on one specific resource prototype
    ResourcePrototype
    A resource prototype is an abstract resource that defines a specific type of resources.
    ResourceView
    A resourceView is a wrapper for resources.
